&lt;p&gt;We are seeking enthusiastic &lt;strong&gt;Small Business Account Executives&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Sales Team. In this role, you will be instrumental in helping small businesses leverage HubSpot&#39;s powerful tools and resources to achieve their growth objectives. You will play a key role in providing personalised guidance and support to our valued customers. As a Small Business Account Executive, you’ll run the full sales cycle; from prospecting to close, with a focus on winning new business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive new business and manage end-to-end sales processes to surpass monthly quotas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nurture inbound and outbound leads to establish new deals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop tailored strategies and solutions to help Small Business clients achieve their objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide expert advice on how to best utilise HubSpot&#39;s platform for business growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver compelling product demos tailored to small business decision-makers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to refine our sales strategy in alignment with new offerings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay updated on industry trends and best practices to continuously improve your knowledge and skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are you?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 years outbound SaaS BDR experience or 1+ years quota-carrying sales experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in full sales cycle deal management, ideally with a complex software solution&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong skills in prospecting, nurturing and net new business development within outbound sales contexts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resilient, goal-oriented, and committed to exceeding targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focused on your goals and and the belief that your daily, weekly and monthly activities will help you achieve them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional consultative sales abilities and expertise in closing deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurate forecasting and pipeline management experience working with a high volume of leads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about Small Businesses and Solving for the Customer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the benefits?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary, stock options, and uncapped commissions&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Structured promotions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible work environment with options for remote, in-office, or hybrid work setups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;World class new hire training and onboarding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Education allowance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible Time Off Policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Healthcare and fitness reimbursements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Primary Caregiver Leave (16 weeks) and Secondary Caregiver Leave (6 weeks)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to collaborate with a diverse team aligned with&lt;a href=&quot;https://network.hubspot.com/slides/the-hubspot-culture-code-1f8v20t3a?hubs_signup-cta=careers-nav-homepage&amp;amp;gh_jid=4483362&amp;amp;_ga=2.188831586.83744431

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;***Now accepting applications for an August 4, 2026 start date***&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Small Business Account Executive at HubSpot, you will&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;drive net-new logo acquisition and new revenue growth&lt;/strong&gt; within the 1–50 employee segment. This is a high-velocity, full-cycle sales role focused primarily on &lt;strong&gt;self-sourced outbound prospecting&lt;/strong&gt; and closing new business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle across &lt;strong&gt;~450 accounts&lt;/strong&gt;, building and managing a pipeline that is &lt;strong&gt;80–90% self-generated outbound&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run multiple sales meetings per day, leading high-quality discovery and tailored demos, and closing within an average &lt;strong&gt;30-day sales cycle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently close net-new revenue at or above quota&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At least 1 year&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;of recent experience&lt;/strong&gt; where the majority of quota attainment came from full-cycle, &lt;strong&gt;net-new logo acquisition (not renewals or expansion)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success managing a primarily outbound pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of consistently hitting or exceeding quota&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong consultative selling and closing skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High activity levels, resilience, coachability, and personal accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The cash compensation below includes base salary, on-target commission for employees in eligible roles, and annual bonus targets under HubSpot’s bonus plan for eligible roles. In addition to cash compensation, some roles are eligible to participate in HubSpot’s equity plan to receive restricted stock units (RSUs). Some roles may also be eligible for overtime pay. Individual compensation packages are tailored to your skills, experience, qualifications, and other job-related reasons.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1C1TGMkG5mos30bkgmNIap_sSzr-lCOWF/view?usp=sharing&quot;&gt;This resource&lt;/a&gt; will help guide how we recommend thinking about the range you see. Learn more about HubSpot’s &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hubspot.com/careers-blog/compensation-philosophy&quot;&gt;compensation philosophy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Benefits are also an important piece of your total compensation package. Explore the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hubspot.com/careers/benefits&quot;&gt;benefits and perks&lt;/a&gt; HubSpot offers to help employees grow better.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;At HubSpot, fair compensation practices aren’t just about checking off the box for legal compliance. It’s about living out our value of transparency with our employees, candidates, and community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Annual Cash Compensation Range:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$120,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$154,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we?&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;HubSpot is a leading customer relationship management (CRM) platform for scaling companies. Tens of thousands of customers all over the world use our marketing, sales, and customer success software to grow their businesses. It&#39;s our mission to not just help them grow, but to help them &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;grow better.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At HubSpot, we believe that our values live in our hearts, not our hallways. We want to build a company where people feel empowered to do their best work, wherever they are. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What’s the role?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Account Executive, Small Business to join our highly successful Sales Team. You will use proactive and inbound selling strategies to find and close new business, and increase the customer&#39;s usage of the HubSpot platform over time. You will use your knowledge of digital transformation and change management to act as a trusted advisor and business consultant to the customer, running the sales process end to end with them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will cover Emerging Markets (SEA)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are your responsibilities as an Account Executive?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Run a full sales cycle and close both new business and install base at or above quota on a monthly cadence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Find new prospects from both inbound and self-sourced leads&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Run qualification calls with C-level executives and department leaders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Run online, and occasionally in person, product demonstrations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sell through internal champions to multiple stakeholders, as well as directly to C -level&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work collaboratively with HubSpot&#39;s marketing and technology departments to evolve our sales strategy when new features and products are introduced&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are you?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;2 years+ of full closing experience in the Small Business space with a focus in the SaaS technology industry, preferably with experience in the Emerging Markets (SEA) or North Asia region&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience in a complex selling environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Have presented and pitched to C-level executives on a business change&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Management of monthly and annual pipeline as well as proven accuracy in forecasting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you get to do in this Small Business Account Executive role?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Account Executive at HubSpot, you use inbound selling strategies to find new business and help them grow using HubSpot software. You benefit from inbound leads and partner with Business Development Reps to research prospects and create outreach strategies. You run online demos of the HubSpot software and successfully sell the HubSpot value proposition. Your target clients will largely consist of small and mid-sized businesses. This position would be based out of your home office working in an inside sales model, and it is a full closing role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the responsibilities of a SmalI Business Account Executive?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will get to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quickly identify challenges that our prospective customers face and discover the best inbound marketing solutions for their business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently close new business at or above quota level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nurture relationships with highly qualified opportunities at small and mid-sized companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build relationships with prospects and internal stakeholders to grow new business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively with HubSpot&#39;s marketing and technology departments to evolve our sales strategy when new features and products are introduced&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help shape the future of HubSpot&#39;s mission with your perspectives, ideas, and skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the role requirements?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Candidates must be based in the Netherlands to be considered for a remote opportunity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ year of&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Closing&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Sales&amp;nbsp;experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fluency in English&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fluency in Dutch would be a plus but is not required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unmatched consultative selling and closing skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurate forecasting and pipeline management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of being a high performer (e.g. over quota, President&#39;s Club)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A sharp focus on your goals and a strong approach for achieving them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
